sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1 - Model Registration via REST API
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI)
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MRProxy as model-registry (proxy)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL 3306/TCP<br/>or PostgreSQL 5432/TCP

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS, Platform auth
    IstioGW->>MRProxy: Forward (Istio mTLS)<br/>VirtualService routing
    MRProxy->>DB: INSERT registered_model<br/>DB protocol, Username/password
    DB-->>MRProxy: Result
    MRProxy-->>IstioGW: 201 Created (JSON)
    IstioGW-->>Client: Response
    end

    %% Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over KServe,MRProxy: Flow 2 - InferenceService Reconciliation
    participant KServe as KServe
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant CtrlMgr as controller-manager<br/>8081/TCP health

    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>CtrlMgr: Watch event (ISVC created)<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
    CtrlMgr->>MRProxy: POST /api/.../inference_services<br/>HTTP :8080, Bearer Token
    MRProxy->>DB: INSERT inference_service
    DB-->>MRProxy: Result
    MRProxy-->>CtrlMgr: 201 Created
    CtrlMgr->>K8sAPI: PATCH ISVC (add labels/finalizer)<br/>HTTPS, ServiceAccount
    end

    %% Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
    Note over CSIInit,ModelStorage: Flow 3 - Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    participant CSIInit as CSI Storage Initializer<br/>(KServe init container)
    participant ModelStorage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    CSIInit->>MRProxy: GET model artifact URI<br/>HTTP :8080
    MRProxy->>DB: SELECT model_artifact<br/>DB protocol
    DB-->>MRProxy: Artifact metadata (storage URI)
    MRProxy-->>CSIInit: model-registry:// → s3://bucket/model
    CSIInit->>ModelStorage: Download model files<br/>HTTPS :443, TLS 1.2+, Storage credentials
    ModelStorage-->>CSIInit: Model artifacts
    end

    %% Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job
    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
    Note over AsyncJob,OCIReg: Flow 4 - Async Model Upload Job
    participant AsyncJob as async-upload-job<br/>(Python K8s Job)
    participant SrcStorage as Source Storage<br/>(S3/OCI) 443/TCP
    participant OCIReg as Destination<br/>OCI Registry 443/TCP

    AsyncJob->>SrcStorage: Download model<br/>HTTPS :443, TLS 1.2+, Storage creds
    SrcStorage-->>AsyncJob: Model files
    Note over AsyncJob: Sign model + OCI image
    AsyncJob->>OCIReg: Push OCI artifact<br/>HTTPS :443, TLS 1.2+, Registry creds
    OCIReg-->>AsyncJob: Push success
    AsyncJob->>MRProxy: Register artifact<br/>HTTP :8080, Bearer Token (optional)
    MRProxy-->>AsyncJob: 201 Created
    end

    %% Flow 5: UI Model Browsing
    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
    Note over Browser,CatalogSrv: Flow 5 - UI Model Browsing
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant BFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CatalogSrv as model-catalog-server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry/{name}/registered_models<br/>User token
    BFF->>MRProxy: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Forwarded token
    MRProxy-->>BFF: Models list (JSON)
    BFF-->>Browser: Proxied response

    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/catalog/models<br/>User token
    BFF->>CatalogSrv: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/catalog_models<br/>Forwarded token
    CatalogSrv-->>BFF: Catalog models (JSON)
    BFF-->>Browser: Proxied response

    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/namespaces<br/>User token
    BFF->>K8sAPI: GET namespaces<br/>HTTPS :443, User token
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: Namespace list
    BFF-->>Browser: Accessible namespaces
    end
